t of Houston) has several strong alternatives that provide similar luxury or holistic day spa experiences with massages, facials, and related services. Here are some top options based on local reviews and listings:\n\n- **Spavia Cinco Ranch** (10705 Spring Green Blvd, Suite 600, Katy, TX 77494): A luxury day spa chain location focused on massages, facials, body treatments, and waxing in a relaxing setting. It’s one of the closest matches in style and offerings.[[2]](https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/)\n\n- **Wellness Spa Katy** (1227 Grand West Blvd, B207, Katy, TX 77449): Specializes in solo, couple, and group massages with a medical/wellness background for an elevated experience.[[3]](https://wellnessspakaty.com/)\n\n- **All Is Well Holistic Spa** (2001 Katy Mills Blvd, Suite I, Katy, TX 77494): Highly rated for holistic massages and spa services in a calming atmosphere; frequently praised in local “best of” lists.[[4]](https://alliswellspa.com/)\n\nOther notable mentions in Katy include:\n- Sole Reflextions\n- Head Harmony Spa\n- Medspa at Villagio (more medspa-oriented)\n- Spa World Houston (larger wellness/thermal spa experience)[[5]](https://www.yelp.com/search?cflt=spas&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\nFor the most current availability, hours, menus, or bookings, check the individual spa websites or platforms like Yelp/TripAdvisor, as offerings can vary. Spavia and similar luxury spots are the closest stylistic alternatives to Woodhouse. If you have preferences (e.g., specific treatments, budget, or couples options), more tailored suggestions are possible.","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://locations.woodhousespas.com/texas/houston/10420-louetta-rd/","start_index":215,"end_index":289,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/","start_index":767,"end_index":812,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://wellnessspakaty.com/","start_index":994,"end_index":1029,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_c